title: Inauguration of Joe Biden
added: Traditions predating the January inaugural ceremonies will likely be announced in December 2020.

title: Inauguration of Joe Biden
added: {{quote|"I do solemnly swear (or affirm) that I will faithfully execute the Office of President of the United States, and will to the best of my Ability, preserve, protect and defend the Constitution of the United States."<ref>{{Cite web|url=usa.gov/inauguration|work=United States Government}}</ref>}}
